{"tid":1257130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港陸沉] 港人露營指南","createTime":"2019-06-25T11:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T09:39:21.000Z","uid":13896,"like":391,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a418fd6b4f2881ba0718e17cf3eb0af62770ff","tid":1257130,"uid":13896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:34:13.000Z","msg":"炎炎夏日​，最啱就係一班人去放狗同露營啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日流流長，大家有咩玩好呢？養狗人士除左放狗玩狗外，仲可以一齊討論下點教育狗隻正確行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而無養狗既巴絲都唔緊要，可以一齊自發玩馬拉松式辯論比賽，練習口條同正確說話技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事不宜遲，等我介紹下新手露營有咩注意既地方啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n必帶裝備：<br />\n帳篷、睡墊（瑜珈墊又得）<br />\n食材、狗糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（攜狗人士專用）<br />\n足夠食水，口罩<br />\n電筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（含電池）<br />\n急救包（營地繩多，天黑容易仆街）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請勿生火煮食，免生危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外宣傳一下，嚟緊26號晚愛丁堡廣場，民陣有大型集會，大家記得多多支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb985494b36558714353f65f1cfa8e3c9133eb8","tid":1257130,"uid":258097,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:36:15.000Z","msg":"啱啊，真係要享受下夏天嘅快感，香港人去露營啦"},{"pid":"4d850879286273ff176fb8ebe1b5ab0f95f553ac","tid":1257130,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a08734e23cbbc66df1716adf12fadabd914985","tid":1257130,"uid":71872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:41:07.000Z","msg":"行得㗎啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f789272d3f935b8c6b83f8be97c43ed0de6e84","tid":1257130,"uid":235796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:43:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"481b038f6949138b1ed9b5089ff8de7c1a96e0ae","tid":1257130,"uid":94794,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:45:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"67f4a625aaa54785c10b8ceff604ddb24c895970","tid":1257130,"uid":94794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b49ba4e40fd2f0dbb52cf6b52a2733bc1bf917f5","tid":1257130,"uid":13896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"10連"},{"pid":"5e5ff6a041b6739b691c8a938eff6569103f1315","tid":1257130,"uid":57643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5cd82a56e4299a65fceb7d77723a237979e8541","tid":1257130,"uid":94794,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:49:57.000Z","msg":"撚狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379ab67019e75f896dc38b85d31ce581ae9dbc99","tid":1257130,"uid":30402,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"我最撚鍾意就係野餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c093e15cd2f99139d80e27d6a2ee994221d72086","tid":1257130,"uid":94794,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:51:19.000Z","msg":"此帖必火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac43e3007bbba71baea111c666e0cbdd241fe70f","tid":1257130,"uid":30402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:51:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{